title: "It's Not My Problem" (Activism & Vegans in Chiang Mai)
description: The Problem With "It's Not My Problem."  This discussion address a range of political issues (and the difficulty activists have in addressing them, or in overcoming public indifference to them), with veganism and ecology being referred to repeatedly (but not exclusively).  There's also some discussion (en passant) of vegans here in Chiang Mai, Thailand, where the video was recorded.
